# Creating a Blog with Velt

<Callout type_="success">
Build beautiful, fast blog sites with Velt's blog theme. Zero JavaScript, lightning-fast load times.
</Callout>

## Quick Start

Get your blog running in 30 seconds:

```bash
# Create a new blog project
velt new my-blog --theme blog

# Navigate to the directory
cd my-blog

# Start the development server
velt dev
```

Your blog is now live at `http://localhost:3000`!

