## Directory Structure

```
my-blog/
├── content/
│   ├── index.vdx              # Home page (post listing)
│   └── posts/
│       ├── hello-world.vdx    # Your first post
│       └── second-post.vdx    # More posts...
├── layouts/
│   ├── post.v                 # Individual post layout
│   └── list.v                 # Post listing layout
├── components/
│   └── PostCard.v             # Post preview card
└── assets/
    └── blog.css               # Custom styles
```

