## Customization

### Theme Variables

Customize your blog's look in `assets/blog.css`:

```css
:root {
  /* Brand colors */
  --blog-accent: #6366f1;
  --blog-accent-hover: #4f46e5;
  
  /* Typography */
  --blog-title-size: 2.5rem;
  --blog-content-width: 720px;
  
  /* Card styling */
  --blog-card-radius: 12px;
  --blog-card-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
```

### Post Title Styling

```css
.post-title {
  font-size: var(--blog-title-size);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
```

### Card Hover Effects

```css
.post-card {
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--blog-card-radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.post-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: var(--blog-card-shadow);
  border-color: var(--blog-accent);
}
```

