## Adding Components

### Tag Component

Create reusable components like tags:

```v
// components/Tag.v
module components

pub struct Tag {
pub:
  name string
  color string = "primary"
}

pub fn (t Tag) render() string {
  return '<span class="tag tag-${t.color}">${t.name}</span>'
}
```

Usage in your posts:

```markdown
<Tag name="Tutorial" color="blue" />
<Tag name="Velt" color="purple" />
```

